{"tid":2424523,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"忘記唔到嘅人  求救","createTime":"2021-02-26T15:29:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T05:24:07.000Z","uid":17554,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3e30ed05ee4a31035d79ec644dfd3e861ecfd1b6","tid":2424523,"uid":17554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T15:29:51.000Z","msg":"大概係咁嘅<br />\n<br />\n呢個同事上年年尾入嚟既 本身打算出發去外國兩三年 之後先會返香港 但因為疫情既問題佢出發唔到 搞到佢要不斷延遲起行<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好衰唔衰我又係呢個時間鍾意咗佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪等佢到時離開就move on 到 但真心我覺得佢係我見過入面最啱既人 但無奈啲timing 錯曬 真係the right person but the wrong timing<br />\n<br />\n你哋覺得我應該let it go 定喺佢走之前同佢攤牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但我又唔想畀太大壓力佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e66379fbc3fe63e8a1c947c417c7160cfb61648b","tid":2424523,"uid":17554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T15:30:06.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推 求意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f9f6721cebaf40e6b75490720e373b65041157a","tid":2424523,"uid":66701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T15:32:22.000Z","msg":"重點係佢點睇你先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算岩timing. 佢未必都當你right person"},{"pid":"dcdad3962e4d696402a1fbe8ed8b1d10aea24464","tid":2424523,"uid":17554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f9f6721cebaf40e6b75490720e373b65041157a","tid":2424523,"uid":66701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T15:32:22.000Z","msg":"重點係佢點睇你先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算岩timing. 佢未必都當你right person"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T15:35:11.000Z","msg":"其實都係 我都唔太知佢點睇我 但感覺佢都好關心我同成日開口埋口讚我呢樣又叫我試下唔同野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src